  "local_port": 40532,
  "remote_port": 443,
  "prompt": "How can I apply for my car to be on Overhaulin'?",
  "response": "To apply for your car to be featured on \"Overhaulin',\" you can follow these steps:\n\n1. **Check Eligibility**: Ensure your car qualifies. Typically, the show looks for older cars that are in need of a serious makeover but still have potential. The car should also have some sentimental value or a compelling story behind it.\n\n2. **Visit the Official Website**: Go to the official website of \"Overhaulin'\" or the network that airs the show (such as MotorTrend). Look for a section labeled \"Casting,\" \"Submissions,\" or \"Apply.\"\n\n3. **Fill Out the Application**: Complete the application form. You'll likely need to provide:\n   - Details about your car, including make, model, year, and current condition.\n   - A personal story about why you want your car to be overhauled.\n   - Photos of your car from multiple angles.\n   - Your contact information.\n\n4. **Submit Additional Materials**: Some applications might require additional materials, such as a short video explaining your story and why you think your car deserves to be on the show.\n\n5. **Wait for a Response**: After submitting your application, you'll need to wait for the casting team to review it. If they're interested, they'll contact you for further steps, which may include an interview or additional information.\n\n6. **Be Patient and Persistent**: The selection process can be competitive and may take some time. If you don't get selected, you can try applying again for future seasons.\n\nRemember, the show may have specific criteria and processes that can change, so always refer to the most current information on their official channels.",
